Package dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.editor Description

Guided Configuration Widgets

This package contains the custom module editor. A custom module editor is thought as a replacement for the generic module editor. It can be used inside a module definition extension point. So the wizard's trigger is shown inside the module configuration area in the project explorer as if it was a normal module editor.

  • GuidedConfigEditor: The custom module editor.
